snippet.title: MenoftheInfinite
snippet.description:
Your Dedicated Wisdom Channel

New Brother Channel - "Men of the Finite"

http://www.youtube.com/MenoftheFinite

If you wish to engage in more indepth discussion of any presentation on this channel, start a thread at Genius Forum:

http://www.theabsolute.net/phpBB/index.php

Please note:  now that the channel has grown a little I am receiving an increased level of correspondence, which is welcome.  However, it's possible that I will from time to time lose track of discussions.  If this happens and you wish for any discussion to continue, feel free to drop me a reminder note.  Thanks.
